===Disney-HIKKY collaboration world===
A limited-time VRChat world, [https://vrchat.com/home/world/wrld_b1b3531a-b498-4411-86bd-3a214a0bbf4f 『トロン：アレス』in VR Shibuya], collaboratively designed by Disney Enterprises<ref>[https://www.disney.co.jp/movie/tron-ares/news/20250918_01 <nowiki>[Japanese]</nowiki> " '渋谷' がデジタル世界に侵食される―公開記念イベント開催！" (Shibuya Goes Digital - public commemorative event held!)] on ''[https://www.disney.co.jp Disney.co.jp]''. Dated September 18, 2025. Retrieved September 22, 2025.</ref>, and HIKKY<ref>[https://hikky.co.jp/en/service HIKKY Services - Overcoming Boundaries Between Virtual and Real Worlds] on ''[https://hikky.co.jp Hikky.co.jp]''. Retrieved September 20, 2025.</ref> (see: [[Community: Virtual Market]]) was launched on September 19, 2025, to promote and commemorate the release of [[Wikipedia:Tron:_Ares|Tron: Ares]]<ref>[https://movies.disney.com/tron-ares "Tron: Ares | Disney Movies"] on ''[https://movies.disney.com Disney.com]''. Retrieved September 22, 2025.</ref>.

This world was promoted by VRChat<ref>[https://bsky.app/profile/vrchat.com/post/3lz6itdcths2m "The Tron: Ares inspired world is live!"] on ''[https://bsky.app/profile/vrchat.com Bluesky]''. Dated September 19, 2025. Retrieved September 20, 2025.</ref><ref>[https://x.com/VRChat/status/1969107865404162507 "Come join us as we check out Sanrio VFes, the Virtual Market "Tron: Ares" inspired world, and more."] on ''[https://https://x.com/VRChat X.com]''. Dated September 19, 2025. Retrieved September 20, 2025.</ref>, and Vket<ref>[https://virtual-market.prezly.com/disney-takes-on-a-new-visual-revolution-tron-ares-takes-over-virtual-shibuya "Disney Takes on a New Visual Revolution! Tron: Ares Takes Over Virtual Shibuya"] on ''[https://virtual-market.prezly.com Prezly]''. Dated September 18, 2025. Retrieved September 20, 2025.</ref><ref>[https://x.com/enVket/status/1968588122276458789 "Disney Takes on a new Visual Revolution! Tron: Ares Takes Over Virtual Shibuya"] on ''[https://https://x.com/enVket X.com]''. Dated on September 18, 2025. Retrieved September 20, 2025.</ref><ref>[https://www.instagram.com/p/DOxyBA9j9q9/ "The Tron: Ares world is available on VRChat for a limited time until 10/31 JST!"] on ''[https://www.instagram.com/vket_official/ Instagram]''. Dated September 18, 2025. Retrieved September 20, 2025.</ref> social media profiles. This world contains a special version of Battle Discs, titled "R3 Lite", by xd_inc. The promotional world was only available to the public for a limited time, until October 31, 2025.
